---
// あかお × おナガ の会話形式でゲームを紹介するコンポーネント
import PixelChara from "./PixelChara.astro";
import PixelOnaga from "./PixelOnaga.astro";

interface Line {
  speaker: "akao" | "onaga";
  text: string;
}

interface Props {
  lines: Line[];
}

const { lines } = Astro.props;
const names: Record<Line["speaker"], string> = {
  akao: "あかお",
  onaga: "おナガ",
};
---

<div class="dialogue">
  {
    lines.map((line) => (
      <div class={`dialogue-row ${line.speaker}`}>
        <div class="dialogue-avatar">
          <div class="dialogue-face">
            {line.speaker === "akao" ? (
              <PixelChara size={34} />
            ) : (
              <PixelOnaga size={46} />
            )}
          </div>
          <span class="dialogue-name">{names[line.speaker]}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="dialogue-bubble">{line.text}</p>
      </div>
    ))
  }
</div>

<style>
  .dialogue {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 24px 0 36px;
  }

  .dialogue-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .dialogue-row.onaga {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .dialogue-avatar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    gap: 6px;
    width: 64px;
  }

  .dialogue-face {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
  }

  .dialogue-row.onaga .dialogue-face {
    background: var(--sky);
  }

  .dialogue-name {
    display: block;
    max-width: 100%;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .dialogue-bubble {
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    max-width: calc(100% - 160px);
    background: #fff;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* アバター側に向く吹き出しのしっぽ */
  .dialogue-bubble::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px;
    left: -14px;
    width: 17px;
    height: 14px;
    background: inherit;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    border-right: none;
  }

  .dialogue-row.onaga .dialogue-bubble {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .dialogue-row.onaga .dialogue-bubble::before {
    left: auto;
    right: -14px;
    border-right: 3px solid var(--ink);
    border-left: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .dialogue-bubble {
      max-width: calc(100% - 76px);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }
  }
</style>
